"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-paralympics-vanderson-chaves-paris-2024-paralympics-fencing-b2542074.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Vanderson Chaves has been forced to improvise as he attempts to make the Paralympics  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 407, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanderson_Scardovelli\", \"score\": 0.9999999375495483, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vanderson\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanderson_Scardovelli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanderson_Scardovelli\"}, {\"begin\": 226, \"end\": 232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"score\": 0.9999999983338057, \"rank\": 1.6663539597182315e-09, \"text\": \"Chaves\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Vanderson Chaves has faced many challenges in more than a decadeas a Paralympic fencer, but none as fearsome as the massive floods inBrazil's Rio Grande do Sul state.\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 598, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 432, \"end\": 441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanderson_Scardovelli\", \"score\": 0.9999999375495483, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vanderson\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanderson_Scardovelli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vanderson_Scardovelli\"}, {\"begin\": 442, \"end\": 448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"score\": 0.9999999983338057, \"rank\": 1.6663539597182315e-09, \"text\": \"Chaves\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The waters washed away his equipment, dozens of medals, his passport - and might have even thwarted his chances of reaching the ParisParalympicsin September.\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chaves' ground-floor apartment, ideal for his wheelchair, lies in an elevated area ofstate capital Porto Alegre.\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"score\": 0.9999999983338057, \"rank\": 1.6663539597182315e-09, \"text\": \"Chaves\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\"}, {\"begin\": 858, \"end\": 870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porto_Alegre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9264353155634417e-20, \"text\": \"Porto Alegre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porto_Alegre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porto_Alegre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Still, that did not spare him from becoming one of the230,000 people displacedby the floodwaters.\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 970, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Days later, his home remains submerged, his few remaining belongings fit in a car, and it's affecting his mental health ahead of two key competitions next week for him to secure his Paralympics berth.\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 1171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no way this would not affect me.\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To compete and to train well, you need to be well psychologically.\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am not,\\\" Chaves toldThe Associated Pressat the Gremio Nautico Uniao, a club that has been turned into shelter for about 300 people since the floods began.\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I come from an impoverished area of Porto Alegre.\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1481, \"end\": 1493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porto_Alegre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9264353155634417e-20, \"text\": \"Porto Alegre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porto_Alegre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porto_Alegre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everything for me is more difficult to achieve.\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1542, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am Black, I am disabled.\", \"from\": 1543, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And now this.\\\"\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1584, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fencer competed at theParalympic Gamesin Rio de Janeiro in 2016 andat Tokyo in 2021.For many years, he has been among the best in the Americas in foil and sabre competitions.\", \"from\": 1586, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1660, \"end\": 1665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_Station\", \"score\": 0.762528838146772, \"rank\": 0.24877250728409805, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_Station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_Station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He needs to score a few more points in two competitions in Sao Paulo to ensure he gets to travel to Paris.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1871, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1824, \"end\": 1833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e3o_Paulo\", \"score\": 0.9858779573453796, \"rank\": 0.012363781011925925, \"text\": \"Sao Paulo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e3o_Paulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e3o_Paulo\"}, {\"begin\": 1865, \"end\": 1870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999022293, \"rank\": 9.777205618589545e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And to get that ticket, he will have to count on donated gear and an unexpectedly tiresome trip because Porto Alegre's airport is flooded, too.\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1976, \"end\": 1988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porto_Alegre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9264353155634417e-20, \"text\": \"Porto Alegre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porto_Alegre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porto_Alegre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chaves will travel from Porto Alegre to Florianopolis on Tuesday in a minivan for about 6 hours and 460 kilometers (287 miles).\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2017, \"end\": 2023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"score\": 0.9999999983338057, \"rank\": 1.6663539597182315e-09, \"text\": \"Chaves\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\"}, {\"begin\": 2041, \"end\": 2053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porto_Alegre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9264353155634417e-20, \"text\": \"Porto Alegre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porto_Alegre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Porto_Alegre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then he will take a short flight to Sao Paulo, so he can compete from Thursday into the weekend.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2181, \"end\": 2190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e3o_Paulo\", \"score\": 0.9858779573453796, \"rank\": 0.012363781011925925, \"text\": \"Sao Paulo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e3o_Paulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/S\\u00e3o_Paulo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His main rivals, who come from Argentina and the US, will be training and fine-tuning until then as they seek to overtake the Brazilian in the world rankings and reach Paris.\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2273, \"end\": 2282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\", \"score\": 0.9996342776510868, \"rank\": 0.0003658561177784609, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\"}, {\"begin\": 2291, \"end\": 2293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 0.9999992124538412, \"rank\": 7.872272146347326e-07, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}, {\"begin\": 2410, \"end\": 2415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999022293, \"rank\": 9.777205618589545e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went to my mother-in-law's house, this is my first day back at the club.\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is like war here, I do not even know whether I would have my mind to train,\\\" said Chaves, who has needed a wheelchair since an accident with a firearm at age 12.\", \"from\": 2494, \"to\": 2658, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2579, \"end\": 2585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"score\": 0.9999999983338057, \"rank\": 1.6663539597182315e-09, \"text\": \"Chaves\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But if there was some training I would be here, that was always my outlet.\\\"\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is little chance that he will return to his apartment anytime soon, with heavy rains still no the forecast.\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why authorities are rushing to rescue survivors of massive flooding that has killed at least 100 people and left another 130 missing.\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some residents have refused to abandon their belongings.\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3048, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Others are returning to evacuated homes despite the risk of new storms.\", \"from\": 3049, \"to\": 3120, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Storms were expected in the state on Thursday, with hail and high wind.\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chaves' coach, Eduardo Nunes, says the Brazilian fencer will face trouble beyond the mental stress and the unexpectedly long trip in his attempt to qualify for the Paralympics.\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3195, \"end\": 3201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"score\": 0.9999999983338057, \"rank\": 1.6663539597182315e-09, \"text\": \"Chaves\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\"}, {\"begin\": 3210, \"end\": 3217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eduardo_Bolsonaro\", \"score\": 0.9998711118040957, \"rank\": 0.0001288978519076806, \"text\": \"Eduardo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eduardo_Bolsonaro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eduardo_Bolsonaro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He will have new gloves.\", \"from\": 3373, \"to\": 3398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For a soccer player, that's like having new boots.\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3449, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He could get blisters with that, the gloves will not be softened.\", \"from\": 3450, \"to\": 3515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"His outfit also needs to be softened, and he will not have time to do that and get used to moving around with it.\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Those little details will affect him.\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3667, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But he can overcome all that,\\\" Nunes said.\", \"from\": 3668, \"to\": 3710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The toughest thing will still be his mental health.\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To focus on what he needs to focus.\\\"\", \"from\": 3764, \"to\": 3800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fencers from Brazil and the US have offered Chaves clothing and equipment for now.\", \"from\": 3802, \"to\": 3884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3815, \"end\": 3821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9999999893989299, \"rank\": 1.0598664205945931e-08, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 3830, \"end\": 3832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"score\": 0.9999992124538412, \"rank\": 7.872272146347326e-07, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_dollar\"}, {\"begin\": 3846, \"end\": 3852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"score\": 0.9999999983338057, \"rank\": 1.6663539597182315e-09, \"text\": \"Chaves\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If he secures a spot in Paris, Brazil's government will automatically grant him better resources to compete.\", \"from\": 3885, \"to\": 3993, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3909, \"end\": 3914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999022293, \"rank\": 9.777205618589545e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3916, \"end\": 3922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9999999893989299, \"rank\": 1.0598664205945931e-08, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chaves believes his challenges can be turned into positives if he secures his place in Paris.\", \"from\": 3995, \"to\": 4088, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4082, \"end\": 4087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999022293, \"rank\": 9.777205618589545e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He still hopes he can find some of the medals he has won in previous competitions.\", \"from\": 4089, \"to\": 4171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I know that a lot of children, a lot of wheelchair fencers, get inspiration from me,\\\" Chaves said in an emotional tone at the training facility, where donations for homeless people are piling up in the next room.\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4260, \"end\": 4266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"score\": 0.9999999983338057, \"rank\": 1.6663539597182315e-09, \"text\": \"Chaves\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G.D._Chaves\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I motivate them.\", \"from\": 4387, \"to\": 4404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can use this to encourage them, and I can use it to encourage myself to go after this, too.\\\"\", \"from\": 4405, \"to\": 4499, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I like to wake up watching the medals, thinking that the following week there is going to be more medals there.\", \"from\": 4501, \"to\": 4613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's something that gives me extra motivation.\", \"from\": 4614, \"to\": 4662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's because I know that I still have it all there underwater.\\\"\", \"from\": 4663, \"to\": 4732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"AP  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4734, \"to\": 4874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4734, \"end\": 4736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999977501331913, \"rank\": 2.233092047082374e-06, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}]}"